## When not to use this component
Don’t use the collapsible component to hide information that the majority of your users will need to progress with their task.

### Alternative components
[Accordions](/components/accordion), [tabs](/components/tabs) and collapsible all hide sections of content which a user can show or hide.

## Variants
Use the collapsible component instead of [tabs](/components/tabs) or [accordions](/components/accordion) if there is only one section of content that needs to be condensed.
